      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@900&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500&display=swap');\n\n  .mtl-section { position:relative; width:100%; height:100svh; min-height:600px; overflow:hidden; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; }\n  .mtl-bg { position:absolute; inset:0; z-index:0; }\n  .mtl-bg video { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; }\n  .mtl-bg-overlay { position:absolute; inset:0; background:linear-gradient(to bottom,rgba(0,0,0,.35) 0%,rgba(0,0,0,.15) 40%,rgba(0,0,0,.4) 100%); }\n  .mtl-inner { position:relative; z-index:2; width:100%; height:100%; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; padding:64px 24px 48px; box-sizing:border-box; }\n  .mtl-title { font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif; font-weight:900; font-size:clamp(52px,8vw,112px); line-height:.92; letter-spacing:-.01em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#fff; text-align:center; text-shadow:0 2px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.4); transition:opacity .4s,transform .4s; margin:0; }\n  .mtl-title.fade { opacity:0; transform:translateY(-8px); }\n  .mtl-center { display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:32px; }\n  .mtl-icon-wrap { width:80px; height:80px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; }\n  .mtl-icon-wrap img { width:80px; height:80px; object-fit:contain; transition:opacity .4s,transform .4s; animation:mtl-pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite; }\n  .mtl-icon-wrap img.fade { opacity:0; transform:scale(.85); }\n  @keyframes mtl-pulse { 0%,100%{transform:scale(1);filter:drop-shadow(0 0 12px rgba(0,201,192,.5))} 50%{transform:scale(1.06);filter:drop-shadow(0 0 24px rgba(0,201,192,.8))} }\n  .mtl-body { max-width:640px; font-size:clamp(15px,1.6vw,19px); line-height:1.65; color:rgba(255,255,255,.92); text-align:center; text-shadow:0 1px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.5); transition:opacity .4s,transform .4s; margin:0; }\n  .mtl-body.fade { opacity:0; transform:translateY(8px); }\n\n  .mtl-tabs-wrap { display:flex !important; justify-content:center !important; width:100% !important; }\n  .mtl-tabs { display:inline-flex !important; width:auto !important; max-width:none !important; flex:none !important; gap:4px !important; background:rgba(0,0,0,.4) !important; backdrop-filter:blur(16px) !important; -webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(16px) !important; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15) !important; border-radius:999px !important; padding:5px !important; margin:0 !important; }\n  .mtl-tab { display:inline-block !important; width:auto !important; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif !important; font-size:13px !important; font-weight:600 !important; letter-spacing:.06em !important; text-transform:uppercase !important; color:rgba(255,255,255,.75) !important; padding:10px 24px !important; border-radius:999px !important; cursor:pointer !important; border:none !important; background:transparent !important; transition:all .3s !important; white-space:nowrap !important; }\n  .mtl-tab.active { background:#0A0A0A !important; color:#F5E642 !important; font-weight:700 !important; }\n  @media(max-width:600px){ .mtl-inner{padding:48px 16px 36px} .mtl-tab{font-size:11px !important;padding:9px 14px !important} }\n</style>\n\n<section class=\"mtl-section\">\n  <div class=\"mtl-bg\">\n    <video autoplay muted loop playsinline>\n      <source src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/e8ee3d6643dd4869808c72509772a567.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n    </video>\n    <div class=\"mtl-bg-overlay\"></div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"mtl-inner\">\n    <div class=\"mtl-title\" id=\"mtl-title\">EFECTOS INMEDIATOS</div>\n    <div class=\"mtl-center\">\n      <div class=\"mtl-icon-wrap\">\n        <img id=\"mtl-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0784/5848/6820/files/white-benefit-icon-001.webp?v=1776812897\" alt=\"\">\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"mtl-body\" id=\"mtl-body\">La cafeína sublingual entra al torrente sanguíneo en minutos, elevando tu foco y energía de manera limpia. Sin el bajón típico del café, sin azúcar, sin calorías.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"mtl-tabs-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"mtl-tabs\">\n        <button class=\"mtl-tab active\" data-index=\"0\">MINUTOS</button>\n        <button class=\"mtl-tab\" data-index=\"1\">HORAS</button>\n        <button class=\"mtl-tab\" data-index=\"2\">DÍAS</button>\n        <button class=\"mtl-tab\" data-index=\"3\">LARGO PLAZO</button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<script>\n(function() {\n  var data = [\n    { title:'EFECTOS INMEDIATOS', icon:'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0784/5848/6820/files/white-benefit-icon-001.webp?v=1776812897', body:'La cafeína sublingual entra al torrente sanguíneo en minutos, elevando tu foco y energía de manera limpia. Sin el bajón típico del café, sin azúcar, sin calorías.' },\n    { title:'PRODUCTIVIDAD MÁXIMA', icon:'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0784/5848/6820/files/white-benefit-icon-002.webp?v=1776812897', body:'Mantené un estado de flow durante 2-3 horas. Sin jitters, sin nerviosismo. Solo claridad mental sostenida mientras las vitaminas B potencian tu rendimiento.' },\n    { title:'VENTAJAS ACUMULADAS', icon:'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0784/5848/6820/files/white-benefit-icon-003.webp?v=1776812898', body:'El uso consistente ayuda a sostener niveles óptimos de energía. Tu cuerpo aprende a rendir mejor con energía limpia en lugar de estimulantes sintéticos.' },\n    { title:'BENEFICIOS SOSTENIDOS', icon:'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0784/5848/6820/files/white-benefit-icon-004.webp?v=1776812898', body:'A largo plazo, la cafeína natural con vitaminas B apoya la función cognitiva sin dependencia ni tolerancia acelerada. Energía que trabaja para vos, no contra vos.' }\n  ];\n  var titleEl=document.getElementById('mtl-title'), iconEl=document.getElementById('mtl-icon'), bodyEl=document.getElementById('mtl-body');\n  var tabs=document.querySelectorAll('.mtl-tab'), current=0, animating=false;\n  function switchTo(i){\n    if(i===current||animating)return; animating=true;\n    titleEl.classList.add('fade'); iconEl.classList.add('fade'); bodyEl.classList.add('fade');\n    setTimeout(function(){\n      current=i; var d=data[i];\n      titleEl.textContent=d.title; iconEl.src=d.icon; bodyEl.textContent=d.body;\n      tabs.forEach(function(t){t.classList.remove('active')}); tabs[i].classList.add('active');\n      titleEl.classList.remove('fade'); iconEl.classList.remove('fade'); bodyEl.classList.remove('fade');\n      setTimeout(function(){animating=false},400);\n    },400);\n  }\n  tabs.forEach(function(tab){tab.addEventListener('click',function(){switchTo(parseInt(this.dataset.index));});});\n})();\n</script>",
